metadata.name: Admiration to Timeless Woman-Marilyn Monroe
metadata.description:
Photograph of a child who had to immigrate from Syria to Turkey. He asks people for help in order to bring money to his family in a crowded environment. Worried about his future, boy daydreams looking at Marilyn Monroe's photo. 

Camera: Canon EOS 6D
Lens: Canon 24-105 mm
